        "text": "The Lord made not this covenant with our fathers — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, with our remote progenitors, with Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob, but with us, their descendants: or if it be understood as spoken of their immediate parents, it means, according to the Hebrew idiom, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Not with our fathers only, but with us also, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "as ",
        "children": []
      },
